      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CLEO'S STAR (1) comes here following a scorching win over 460m at Geelong in 25.75. Top win latest and looms as the one to beat again. NEO DEVERE (3) has been without a win for a while, the latest jumping from an outside draw when fifth (30.04) at this track in a Grade 5. Solid record here at the distance winning three races. The form out of his last race has been franked. Can measure up this time. PAW SAPPHIRE (2) sprung the lids and on speed throughout before being run over late when fifth (30.45) at The Meadows over 525m. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. O'KEEFE (8) cannot be dismissed although new to this venue.",
